Chalais is home to the "Bibliothèque communale et scolaire de Chalais et Vercorin" library. The library has () 16,102 books or other media, and loaned out 30,421 items in the same year. It was open a total of 191 days with average of 16 hours per week during that year.
Music Video.
The blazon of the municipal coat of arms is "Azure an Ibex rampant Argent on Coupeaux Vert."
Of the population in the village, 110 or about 34.5% were born in Saint-Luc and lived there in 2000. There were 87 or 27.3% who were born in the same canton, while 53 or 16.6% were born somewhere else in Switzerland, and 66 or 20.7% were born outside of Switzerland.

It has a population of about 595 people.
